movie.title: No Name
movie.writer: Matt Brosey, David Fekete, Alexis Johnston
movie.actors: Marshall Dalansky, David Fekete, Kelsey Getz
movie.plot: Jackson, a struggling writer, meets a woman who shares his same passion. Over time, they both share each other's stories, but he never gets her name, until she gets mugged, yet sadly Jackson discovers it out the hard way.
